title: Rubbermaid Commercial 3486592 Flex Wall-Mounted Manual Skin Care Dispenser, Black, 1000- to 1300 mL
features: Large-capacity dispenser delivers the most washes, up to 3,250 per refill. Adjustable portion control with three dose sizes: 0.4, 0.65, or 1.0 mL.

Takes 2 refill sizes to meet any need. Dispenses a broad range of luxurious soaps, sanitizers, and moisturizing lotion. Refills available.
Antimicrobial Push Bar with Silver-Ion Technology reduces cross-contamination. Optional lock plate deters vandalism.
Fully ADA compliant. Color: Black. Capacity: 1000 mL or 1300 mL.
